title: Book of Eli - NTSC
description:
The Book of Eli is the story of Eli, played by Denzel Washington, who lives in a post-apocalyptic America. Eli is entrusted to protect a sacred book, which might hold the key to the survival for the entire human race. He is faced with a new threat when a cunning nemesis, played by Gary Oldman, sets his sights on acquiring the valuable and sacred book by using any means at his disposal.


The DVD has english, spanish and french audio and subtitles.


Enjoy!
